<div id="p1" class="page active">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero1">
    <div class="eyebrow">For Accounting, CPA & Bookkeeping Firm Owners</div>
    <h1 class="h1">Free Calculator.<br><em>See Your Firm's AI Risk Score — and What It's Costing You Not to Automate.</em></h1>
    <p class="h1-sub">Every firm using AI informally is carrying risk nobody's measured. Every firm avoiding it is leaving capacity on the table nobody's counted. Answer a few questions and we'll show you both numbers for your specific firm — in about 3 minutes.</p>
    <a href="#audit-form" class="hero-cta-btn">Calculate My Firm's Number →</a>
    <div class="trust-pills">
      <span class="tpill">Tax Prep</span><span class="tpill">Bookkeeping</span><span class="tpill">Full-Service CPA</span>
      <span class="tpill">Fractional CFO</span><span class="tpill">Payroll</span>
    </div>
    <div class="form-card-wrap" id="audit-form">
      <div class="form-card">
        <div class="form-card-header">
          <div class="form-card-title">🧮 Free Calculator: Your AI Risk & Opportunity Score</div>
          <div class="form-card-sub">Takes about 3 minutes · Results instant · Completely free</div>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" id="progress" style="width:8%"></div></div>

        <div class="form-step active" id="stepQ1">
          <div class="step-counter">Question 1 of 7</div>
          <div class="step-title">How many people work at your firm, including you?</div>
          <div class="step-sub">Drag to the number that matches — we'll use this to scale your results across the whole team.</div>
          <div class="slider-wrap">
            <div class="slider-val"><span id="headcountVal" class="slider-val-num">5</span></div>
            <input type="range" min="1" max="25" value="5" id="headcount" oninput="updateHeadcount(this.value)"/>
            <div class="slider-labels"><span>Just me</span><span>25+</span></div>
          </div>
          <button class="btn" onclick="showStep('stepQ2')">Continue →</button>
        </div>

        <div class="form-step" id="stepQ2">
          <div class="step-counter">Question 2 of 7</div>
          <div class="step-title">How would you describe your firm's current use of AI tools?</div>
          <div class="step-sub">Be honest — this shapes both the opportunity and the risk side of your results.</div>
          <div class="goal-grid">
            <button class="goal-card" onclick="selectAiMaturity(this,0)"><div class="goal-card-title">Not using AI at all</div></button>
            <button class="goal-card" onclick="selectAiMaturity(this,1)"><div class="goal-card-title">A few people use ChatGPT casually, no real structure</div></button>
            <button class="goal-card" onclick="selectAiMaturity(this,2)"><div class="goal-card-title">Some structured use, but no firm-wide strategy</div></button>
            <button class="goal-card" onclick="selectAiMaturity(this,3)"><div class="goal-card-title">We have specific AI tools and workflows already in place</div></button>
          </div>
          <button class="btn" id="q2-next" disabled onclick="showStep('stepQ3a')">Continue →</button>
          <button class="btn-back" onclick="showStep('stepQ1')">← Back</button>
        </div>

        <div class="form-step" id="stepQ3a">
          <div class="step-counter">Question 3 of 7</div>
          <div class="step-title">About how many hours a week does EACH team member spend on repetitive tasks?</div>
          <div class="step-sub">Document chasing, data entry, drafting client emails — the manual stuff, not the judgment calls. We'll apply this across your whole team next.</div>
          <div class="slider-wrap">
            <div class="slider-val"><span id="hoursVal" class="slider-val-num">14</span><span class="slider-val-unit">hrs/week</span></div>
            <input type="range" min="0" max="40" value="14" id="hoursPerPerson" oninput="updateHours(this.value)"/>
            <div class="slider-labels"><span>0</span><span>40+</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="slider-note">14 hrs/week is what we typically see across firms like yours — adjust if yours is different.</div>
          <button class="btn" onclick="showStep('stepQ3b')" style="margin-top:.9rem">Continue →</button>
          <button class="btn-back" onclick="showStep('stepQ2')">← Back</button>
        </div>

        <div class="form-step" id="stepQ3b">
          <div class="step-counter">Question 4 of 7</div>
          <div class="step-title">Which of these usually takes the most time?</div>
          <div class="step-sub">This decides which free tool we recommend on your results page.</div>
          <div class="goal-grid">
            <button class="goal-card" onclick="selectTimeSink(this,'docChasing')"><div class="goal-card-title">Chasing clients for documents</div></button>
            <button class="goal-card" onclick="selectTimeSink(this,'returns')"><div class="goal-card-title">Drafting returns or financial statements</div></button>
            <button class="goal-card" onclick="selectTimeSink(this,'dataEntry')"><div class="goal-card-title">Manual data entry</div></button>
            <button class="goal-card" onclick="selectTimeSink(this,'emails')"><div class="goal-card-title">Drafting client emails & updates</div></button>
            <button class="goal-card" onclick="selectTimeSink(this,'mix')"><div class="goal-card-title">Honestly, a mix of all of it</div></button>
          </div>
          <button class="btn" id="q3b-next" disabled onclick="showStep('stepQ4')">Continue →</button>
          <button class="btn-back" onclick="showStep('stepQ3a')">← Back</button>
        </div>

        <div class="form-step" id="stepQ4">
          <div class="step-counter">Question 5 of 7</div>
          <div class="step-title">Does your firm have a written policy on what client data can and can't be entered into AI tools like ChatGPT?</div>
          <div class="goal-grid">
            <button class="goal-card" onclick="selectPolicy(this,'documented')"><div class="goal-card-title">Yes, documented and everyone's trained on it</div></button>
            <button class="goal-card" onclick="selectPolicy(this,'informal')"><div class="goal-card-title">We have something informal</div></button>
            <button class="goal-card" onclick="selectPolicy(this,'none')"><div class="goal-card-title">No, nothing in writing</div></button>
            <button class="goal-card" onclick="selectPolicy(this,'notsure')"><div class="goal-card-title">Not sure</div></button>
          </div>
          <button class="btn" id="q4-next" disabled onclick="showStep('stepQ5')">Continue →</button>
          <button class="btn-back" onclick="showStep('stepQ3b')">← Back</button>
        </div>

        <div class="form-step" id="stepQ5">
          <div class="step-counter">Question 6 of 7</div>
          <div class="step-title">Are you aware that tax preparers are classified as "financial institutions" under the FTC Safeguards Rule, which requires a written data security program?</div>
          <div class="step-sub">This applies more broadly than most preparers realize.</div>
          <div class="goal-grid">
            <button class="goal-card" onclick="selectFtc(this,'compliant')"><div class="goal-card-title">Yes, and we're confident we're compliant</div></button>
            <button class="goal-card" onclick="selectFtc(this,'unsure')"><div class="goal-card-title">Yes, but not sure if we're fully compliant</div></button>
            <button class="goal-card" onclick="selectFtc(this,'no')"><div class="goal-card-title">No, wasn't aware of this</div></button>
          </div>
          <button class="btn" id="q5-next" disabled onclick="showStep('stepQ6')">Continue →</button>
          <button class="btn-back" onclick="showStep('stepQ4')">← Back</button>
        </div>

        <div class="form-step" id="stepQ6">
          <div class="step-counter">Question 7 of 7</div>
          <div class="step-title">Do you know exactly which AI tools your team is using on client work — or could they be using tools you don't know about?</div>
          <div class="step-sub">Most owners have never actually asked.</div>
          <div class="goal-grid">
            <button class="goal-card" onclick="selectShadow(this,'full')"><div class="goal-card-title">Yes — I know exactly what's being used and how</div></button>
            <button class="goal-card" onclick="selectShadow(this,'partial')"><div class="goal-card-title">I have a general sense, but not the full picture</div></button>
            <button class="goal-card" onclick="selectShadow(this,'noidea')"><div class="goal-card-title">No idea — it could be happening without my knowledge</div></button>
          </div>
          <button class="btn" id="q6-next" disabled onclick="showStep('stepQ7')">Continue →</button>
          <button class="btn-back" onclick="showStep('stepQ5')">← Back</button>
        </div>

        <div class="form-step" id="stepQ7">
          <div class="step-counter">Almost there</div>
          <div class="step-title">What's your biggest concern with AI, if you're honest about it?</div>
          <div class="step-sub">Pick the one that's actually holding you back.</div>
          <div class="goal-grid">
            <button class="goal-card" onclick="selectConcern(this,'privacy')"><div class="goal-card-title">Client & data privacy</div></button>
            <button class="goal-card" onclick="selectConcern(this,'resistance')"><div class="goal-card-title">My team resisting a new way of working</div></button>
            <button class="goal-card" onclick="selectConcern(this,'knowledge')"><div class="goal-card-title">Not knowing enough about the tools to trust them</div></button>
            <button class="goal-card" onclick="selectConcern(this,'startingpoint')"><div class="goal-card-title">Not knowing where to even start</div></button>
            <button class="goal-card" onclick="selectConcern(this,'cost')"><div class="goal-card-title">Cost — not convinced it's worth the investment</div></button>
          </div>
          <button class="btn" id="q7-next" disabled onclick="showStep('stepContact')">Continue →</button>
          <button class="btn-back" onclick="showStep('stepQ6')">← Back</button>
        </div>

        <div class="form-step" id="stepContact">
          <div class="step-counter">Last step</div>
          <div class="step-title">Where should we send your number?</div>
          <div class="step-sub">We'll email your Risk & Opportunity Score, and you can grab a free 20-minute call underneath it.</div>
          <input class="field" type="text" id="fullname" placeholder="Full name" oninput="checkContact()"/>
          <div class="field-error" id="fullname-error">Please enter your first and last name</div>
          <input class="field" type="text" id="bizname" placeholder="Firm name" oninput="checkContact()"/>
          <input class="field" type="email" id="email" placeholder="Firm email address" oninput="checkContact()"/>
          <div class="field-error" id="email-error">Please use your firm email address, not a personal one</div>
          <input class="field" type="tel" id="phone" placeholder="Phone number" oninput="checkContact()"/>
          <div class="field-error" id="phone-error">Enter a valid phone number</div>
          <button class="btn" id="contact-submit" disabled onclick="submitForm()">See My Risk & Opportunity Score →</button>
          <button class="btn-back" onclick="showStep('stepQ7')">← Back</button>
          <p class="micro">Free. Instant. No obligation to book anything.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

